getTemplateByMediaId

public Template getTemplateByMediaId(java.lang.String media_id)
                              throws JSONException
Get the Template that corresponds to a particular media. We only return one Template, but we don't enforce such a relationship in the SQL scheme because there may be more than one template per media in the database (in the future may be allowed to update the templates but still want to keep old ones on hand).

Parameters:
media_id - String Used to uniquely identify the media.
Returns:
Template instances corresponding to the template.
Throws:
JSONException
